"{\"uid\": \"bandt.com.au-an-olympic-effort-kaj-lofgren-on-making-the-yarra-swimmable\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The world watched in wonder and disbelief as Paris set about a major cleanup of the Seine River ahead of theOlympics- from hilarious campaigns to the Mayor of Paris swimming the Seine herself, Olympic organisers went to extreme lengths to prove the cleanliness of the river.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547353592, \"rank\": 4.52646518360049e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547353592, \"rank\": 4.52646518360049e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999990358264869, \"rank\": 8.790579428408075e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Melbourne's Yarra River is set to undergo a rebrand of a similar nature.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since forming in 2020,Regen Melbourneand a committed group of researchers, environmental advocates, Indigenous leaders, engineers, entrepreneurs, and environmentalists have been hatching a plan to make Melbourne's Birrarung (Yarra) River swimmable.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birrarung\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B&T spoke with Regen's CEO, Kaj Lofgren, about how he and his team are tackling this mammoth goal.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B&T\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We started to ask the question: how can we be useful?\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are conscious that we are all members of too many online communities that maybe do not push us to do much - we did not want to be just another network,\\\" said Lofgren.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most social and environmental goals are heavily constricted by funding, culture, and imagination.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These are the issues we were trying to fight against.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We asked our partners to think about solutions as if none of these constraints existed - and the river kept coming up!\\\"\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It came up from different angles, namely as a source of deep connection for many Victorians\\\".\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\", \"score\": 0.9999996986648966, \"rank\": 1.788139042476567e-07, \"text\": \"Victorians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victorian_era\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But also, in a pragmatic sense, most of the water we drink comes from the river,\\\" added Lofgren.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of creating a swimmable corridor from source to sea, Dights Falls to Port Phillip Bay, preoccupied the minds of Lofgren and the Regen Melbourne Alliance.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dights Falls\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dights_Falls\"}, {\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Port Phillip Bay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Phillip\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\", \"score\": 0.6881450014984589, \"rank\": 0.4531821023511726, \"text\": \"Alliance\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barisan_Nasional\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swimmable Birrarung initiative is part of a growing global trend of city river cleanups, namely the highly publicised cleanup of the Seine River ahead of the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547353592, \"rank\": 4.52646518360049e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around \\u20ac1.4b (AUD $2.3b) has resulted in the water now being bacteria-free 90 per cent of the time.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, it was ravaged by E. coli and enterococci.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The cleanup of the Seine River is deeply inspiring.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both because of the successful outcome, a swimmable river, but also at a broader level - it's a reminder we can do big things when we put our minds to it,\\\" said Lofgren.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oslo, Copenhagen, Vienna, Switzerland, and closer to home, Sydney's Parramatta River, are all success stories of urban river swimming.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\", \"score\": 0.9999976682452043, \"rank\": 2.2867256268343173e-06, \"text\": \"Oslo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oslo\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\", \"score\": 0.9999999085744136, \"rank\": 5.099983380704096e-08, \"text\": \"Copenhagen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Copenhagen\"}, {\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"score\": 0.9999990926680336, \"rank\": 9.07328447954746e-07, \"text\": \"Vienna\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999912445133702, \"rank\": 8.155036062615158e-06, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999878000388215, \"rank\": 1.2160825851777794e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nursing yourself in water is perhaps the most visceral way of being reminded of the fact that we are nature.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no other feeling like that,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have worked in many complex project environments where burnout and overwhelm are high, and that's the first thing that stops meaningful action,\\\" Lofgren said.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To counter this, Lofgren and his team created six fields of action that made the Swimmable Birrarung initiative more digestible.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Birrarung\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fields of action also allow partners to quickly get involved by recognising how their skills can best be used.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fields are storytelling, legal and policy, water health, business and enterprise, campaigns, building a movement, and swimming activations.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To build a movement, Regen Melbourne partnered with Yarra Riverkeeper Association (YRKA) on the Birrarung Riverfest, a 3-week-long celebration of the Birrarung River and its importance to the city.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999880298539866, \"rank\": 1.1970289211237777e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"score\": 0.9999996638244394, \"rank\": 3.361756957281036e-07, \"text\": \"Yarra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yarra_River\"}, {\"begin\": 3029, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverkeeper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Riverkeeper\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverkeeper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverkeeper\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B&T spoke with Carolyn Tate, event producer at YRKA for this year's Riverfest.\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3169, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B&T\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Br\\u00fcgger_&_Thomet\"}, {\"begin\": 3184, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"score\": 0.9996931906672973, \"rank\": 0.00015844870422718348, \"text\": \"Carolyn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolyn_Culliton\"}, {\"begin\": 3192, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\", \"score\": 0.6985519623656926, \"rank\": 0.4314791256772785, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate_Modern\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Riverfest was identified as a powerful point because of the orientation it gave people to the importance of the river in their everyday lives\\\".\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The event has brought together lots of exciting partners.\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We work with Riverfest as a strategic partner - our role is to convene and rally others to partake and add to the growing event\\\".\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lofgren identified funding, culture, and imagination as three critical blockages to achieving big things.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagination was a particularly powerful one, he argued.\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are suffering from an imagination deficit at the moment.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could well be our biggest hurdle.\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have choices as humans living in cities, and we need to reclaim our choices,\\\" said Lofgren.\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imagination and creativity are what media and comms people are brilliant at.\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 4022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I suspect it's an underestimated superpower.\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Small contributions at the right time can have a massive impact,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The media industry has a significant role to play when it comes to challenging assumptions and helping to encourage positive changes through its storytelling capabilities.\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need comms and creative people to make campaigns that answer questions like, what is the narrative of our city?\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's our message?\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These narratives can have real implications and create positive change\\\".\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No related posts.\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign in to your account  Username or Email Address  Password  Remember Me\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": []}]}"